{"tid":27061,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"【健身】新手增肌 , 單練時點樣揀一個安全又有效果嘅啞鈴重量","createTime":"2016-12-07T06:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T11:38:45.000Z","uid":25468,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a831e655dd99d122401b0873fd5ea889930a4b26","tid":27061,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:04:58.000Z","msg":"舉鐵一般得3 個目的<br />\n健力(練大力) , 增肌 , 修身<br />\n<br />\n而新手多數以增肌做首要目的 , 增肌運動 , 動作重覆次數同動作幅度比啞鈴重量重要<br />\n<br />\n揀啞鈴重量 , 你首先要知道何謂 1RM , 1RM 意思係你做某動作時 , 只可以以某啞鈴重量正確地做一下的動作<br />\n<br />\n例如你練老鼠仔 , 用20磅只能彎舉一下 , 第二下已經要 chok , 咁我就會定你個二頭肌(老鼠仔)個 1RM 係20磅 , 咁你之後想練大老鼠仔 , 就以 1RM 嘅 55-60% 重量去練 , 20磅嘅 60%係 12磅 , 如果間 gym 無 12磅鈴 , 咁就用 10磅去練 , 盡量唔好低過 1RM 嘅 50% , 如是者你就用 10 磅啞鈴做 10下彎舉 , 做完就休息 60-90秒 , 共做 4 sets<br />\n<br />\n做動作時唔好偷雞 , 幅度要做足全程 , 做半程係練其他野的<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.jianshen8.com/uploads/allimg/130721/2_130721215703_2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jianshen8.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F130721%2F2_130721215703_2.gif&h=9853e8ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新手基本上鳩練都會有效果 , 因為平時肌肉少運動 , 一運動就反應好大 , 你新玩可能會發現 1RM 會升得好快 , 但3-6個月就會慢番 , 到時就要轉一轉訓練方式 , 例如增加動作及重覆次數"},{"pid":"2d992df8143934cb336b7a87e0eda46a2d305f41","tid":27061,"uid":32322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:09:06.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"b125a13c514b3e58f245aa21a95de6d24c77469f","tid":27061,"uid":3488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:24:24.000Z","msg":"lm 想練手臂同老鼠仔"},{"pid":"2eb27f91e2431f5eff3501f7b494b9e898089550","tid":27061,"uid":4236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:25:56.000Z","msg":"有無多d二頭練既動作<br />\n同埋三頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a73a8085f6ecf3135a225b5e83153ed4495850","tid":27061,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:30:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無多d二頭練既動作<br />\n<br />\n同埋三頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就咁睇 , 新仔練三頭做掌上壓就夠 , 之後推胸都會練到三頭 , 到推胸推到新手平台期先分開三頭獨立練都得"},{"pid":"cbaf6b7368b8fb61f9d72cfc23486b7e141376fd","tid":27061,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:39:44.000Z","msg":"以 1RM 55-60% 練完<br />\n每組細肌肉做完最少休息 48小時 , 大肌肉做完最少休息 72 小時"},{"pid":"6b827f34d8e9caf691a2426e38a876eea2623912","tid":27061,"uid":18432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:47:29.000Z","msg":"想請教新手點練好？<br />\n有無schedule介紹<br />\n如 day 1 做d咩動作，練邊幾part肌肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f57cd40192e638fc8e6f0e3b60c5513b5ebb30","tid":27061,"uid":40348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:50:38.000Z","msg":"想問平時推完胸<br />\n<br />\n另一日唔係個胸 痛<br />\n<br />\n係2頭痛<br />\n<br />\n點先可以集中返係個胸到<br />\n<br />\n平時做都FEEL到係2頭用力多"},{"pid":"2ccd954558724613ce87fe9a7ff724bfd408e5a4","tid":27061,"uid":40503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:54:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問平時推完胸<br />\n<br />\n另一日唔係個胸 痛<br />\n<br />\n係2頭痛<br />\n<br />\n點先可以集中返係個胸到<br />\n<br />\n平時做都FEEL到係2頭用力多</blockquote><br />\n二頭？你做db fly?"},{"pid":"bc86601c8fbd808eebdfdf9afc058e5a75e7b003","tid":27061,"uid":4236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:55:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無多d二頭練既動作<br />\n<br />\n同埋三頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就咁睇 , 新仔練三頭做掌上壓就夠 , 之後推胸都會練到三頭 , 到推胸推到新手平台期先分開三頭獨立練都得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都做左一段時間了  唔算新仔<br />\n但二頭同三頭進展差"},{"pid":"f651a3ece96dc6bcb9f04a54e69e2fa37f0896c7","tid":27061,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T07:00:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問平時推完胸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一日唔係個胸 痛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係2頭痛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點先可以集中返係個胸到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平時做都FEEL到係2頭用力多</blockquote><br />\n推胸有樣野好重要, 就係手指要虛握 , 即係手指唔會揸死條bar , 會輕微放鬆手指但又唔會跌bar , 你玩輕啲感受一下個感覺先 , 其實推幾下前臂就酸到仆街就代表手指握得太緊, 用左臂力黎推 , 咁樣推一世胸都唔會大"},{"pid":"ca5f5498720dd94cd9e02f4bf99217023337f0c3","tid":27061,"uid":54708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T07:05:51.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d0f28f4f6f7aa7c46f36dc1eb965a6c39caab1bc","tid":27061,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T07:08:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無多d二頭練既動作<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋三頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就咁睇 , 新仔練三頭做掌上壓就夠 , 之後推胸都會練到三頭 , 到推胸推到新手平台期先分開三頭獨立練都得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都做左一段時間了  唔算新仔<br />\n<br />\n但二頭同三頭進展差</blockquote><br />\n二頭過左新手期 , 就要加動作 , 一般用3 個動作去操<br />\n將二頭中嘅長短兩頭分開練<br />\n<br />\n牧師椅彎舉 , 斜椅後傾彎舉 , 單手大脾內側集中妤舉<br />\n<br />\n希望你知我講邊3 個動作"},{"pid":"6a6fe9ed9dffbfc6f0cc2707f7d50ebda5ab4944","tid":27061,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:43:38.000Z","msg":"二頭肌訓練3 動作<br />\n<br />\n針對二頭肌長頭 (外面果part , 二頭中最弱)<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.gymbeginner.hk/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/incline-offset-thumb-dumbbell-curl_470x360_11-e1415619878171.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gymbeginner.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F05%2Fincline-offset-thumb-dumbbell-curl_470x360_11-e1415619878171.jpg&h=8c0c0d23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n針對二頭肌短頭 (埋邊果part)<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.jianshen8.com/uploads/allimg/130721/2_130721214719_1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jianshen8.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F130721%2F2_130721214719_1.gif&h=1de679a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n集中彎舉 , 兩個頭都練 , 一般可以舉重少少<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.jianshen8.com/uploads/allimg/130721/2_130721215703_2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jianshen8.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F130721%2F2_130721215703_2.gif&h=9853e8ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af90964203655a52bd342b3e393230d79784240f","tid":27061,"uid":52824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:43:37.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"fc4d4d81c25ad912b85bb4bde952695983385fdb","tid":27061,"uid":30228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:48:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>二頭肌訓練3 動作<br />\n<br />\n針對二頭肌長頭 (外面果part , 二頭中最弱)<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.gymbeginner.hk/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/incline-offset-thumb-dumbbell-curl_470x360_11-e1415619878171.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gymbeginner.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F05%2Fincline-offset-thumb-dumbbell-curl_470x360_11-e1415619878171.jpg&h=8c0c0d23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n針對二頭肌短頭 (埋邊果part)<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.jianshen8.com/uploads/allimg/130721/2_130721214719_1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jianshen8.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F130721%2F2_130721214719_1.gif&h=1de679a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n集中彎舉 , 兩個頭都練 , 一般可以舉重少少<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.jianshen8.com/uploads/allimg/130721/2_130721215703_2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jianshen8.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F130721%2F2_130721215703_2.gif&h=9853e8ce&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中間個part 舉完好High <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d0d1e08d17bcb57d264c1f46cf6f02348f4219f","tid":27061,"uid":4236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:49:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>二頭肌訓練3 動作<br />\n<br />\n針對二頭肌長頭 (外面果part , 二頭中最弱)<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.gymbeginner.hk/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/incline-offset-thumb-dumbbell-curl_470x360_11-e1415619878171.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gymbeginner.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F05%2Fincline-offset-thumb-dumbbell-curl_470x360_11-e1415619878171.jpg&h=8c0c0d23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n針對二頭肌短頭 (埋邊果part)<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.jianshen8.com/uploads/allimg/130721/2_130721214719_1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jianshen8.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F130721%2F2_130721214719_1.gif&h=1de679a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n集中彎舉 , 兩個頭都練 , 一般可以舉重少少<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.jianshen8.com/uploads/allimg/130721/2_130721215703_2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jianshen8.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F130721%2F2_130721215703_2.gif&h=9853e8ce&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該曬巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"366038be7449db2fffa3d3f5df139c5d5ee4481d","tid":27061,"uid":1646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:54:34.000Z","msg":"Lm學野"},{"pid":"542f92668d6aa85b7de64833f340ac869cb8c0aa","tid":27061,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T12:06:30.000Z","msg":"背好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n背係咪下數多比較重要"},{"pid":"e554c17111de9b2f3134d9560a57cd4911fc87e9","tid":27061,"uid":30800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T12:17:32.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"87d374d16131d17481f7f0e5c5fd7247fa98bc2a","tid":27061,"uid":21775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:26:08.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"7fc4554a4ef971af969016ee5abf21501ab80122","tid":27061,"uid":37380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:56:16.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"215936547e54c3424d5f73a4a27dc65f752d3516","tid":27061,"uid":40348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:57:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問平時推完胸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一日唔係個胸 痛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係2頭痛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點先可以集中返係個胸到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平時做都FEEL到係2頭用力多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n二頭？你做db fly?</blockquote><br />\n用史密斯機. 推完 紅都面晒  同埋係前臂酸到仆街<br />\n<br />\n但前日推完 個胸今日有小小酸<br />\n<br />\n禁落去會小小酸果種  但二頭就真係好撚酸果隻"},{"pid":"aa377103c836d70849440e0d5d3758a1a6132847","tid":27061,"uid":40348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:57:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問平時推完胸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一日唔係個胸 痛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係2頭痛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點先可以集中返係個胸到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平時做都FEEL到係2頭用力多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n二頭？你做db fly?</blockquote><br />\n用史密斯機. 推完 紅都面晒  同埋係前臂酸到仆街<br />\n<br />\n但前日推完 個胸今日有小小酸<br />\n<br />\n禁落去會小小酸果種  但二頭就真係好撚酸果隻"},{"pid":"9f2b89fcbefc443c989ee7e60a58642e3ac731bd","tid":27061,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:10:29.000Z","msg":"史密斯機會推壞手勢，推bar 啦"},{"pid":"51401ea4932a6439a00bc85a1dbd1b025638e488","tid":27061,"uid":58734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:11:40.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"6c9ad77227e25d0b74d151b6cea018a28e9fcb73","tid":27061,"uid":41805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:17:37.000Z","msg":"冇smith machine 得啞鈴 / 凳 / cable machine<br />\n有冇動作練到squad/deadlift 呢d 多種部位？"},{"pid":"65de9ccdec810ad83e17b7ade0d3baf6fa4e153a","tid":27061,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:51:06.000Z","msg":"玩左一對10kg啞鈴幾年 去到某個位真係好難增肌 之後再買左兩對啞鈴黎砌"},{"pid":"4735cc599d570a31efb9959925ec87c044e948dc","tid":27061,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T16:30:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問平時推完胸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一日唔係個胸 痛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係2頭痛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點先可以集中返係個胸到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平時做都FEEL到係2頭用力多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二頭？你做db fly?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用史密斯機. 推完 紅都面晒  同埋係前臂酸到仆街<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但前日推完 個胸今日有小小酸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n禁落去會小小酸果種  但二頭就真係好撚酸果隻</blockquote><br />\n前臂酸係因為用錯力 , 我前面有 reply 你點改 , 你上去睇番啦,<br />\n史密斯個軌跡太固定 , 會不知不覺推大左重量而傷膊的 , 新手有槓鈴最好用槓鈴 , 無就用啞鈴"},{"pid":"a58dd4259f2640a3608fc711e4e117ef946680c0","tid":27061,"uid":42150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:24:59.000Z","msg":"巴打 新手背肌好弱 做兩做拉背機 已經冇力 點操背好？"},{"pid":"2af1e0f45c3d91f748e4309650462764cc2ea876","tid":27061,"uid":50725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:26:06.000Z","msg":"新天新地<br />\n歡迎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5e810cf7fd0192359509736352a1a5ebf9fa80","tid":27061,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:30:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打 新手背肌好弱 做兩做拉背機 已經冇力 點操背好？</blockquote><br />\n新手好多肌肉都未 wake up , 唔好怕肉酸拉輕磅啲先 , 盡量6sets 內完成 40下 , 我新手果時玩拉背機都只係拉自己體重一半 , 而第一個目標係自己體重 , 努力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2966c77b91d482be841935618be308d04999c7d","tid":27061,"uid":42150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:55:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打 新手背肌好弱 做兩做拉背機 已經冇力 點操背好？</blockquote><br />\n新手好多肌肉都未 wake up , 唔好怕肉酸拉輕磅啲先 , 盡量6sets 內完成 40下 , 我新手果時玩拉背機都只係拉自己體重一半 , 而第一個目標係自己體重 , 努力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實做掌上壓 可唔可以強化背肌？<br />\n我想背肌有返d力先再做拉背機"},{"pid":"f22b6952cd39f13f6517710792f428b011f8a900","tid":27061,"uid":8149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:56:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">_ _ _ _，_ _ _ _！</span></span>"},{"pid":"f0480bd668c0bf9cafe7ccf0d00589796cd96d89","tid":27061,"uid":30998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"